{"tid":16135,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：中國新登記知識產權數字世界第一","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T12:27:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd9370f77ce8086c211519b617dedc59e7af4b0","tid":16135,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:15:36.000Z","msg":"梁振英出席香港經濟峰會時，花約半個小時就經濟問題發表演說。繼他周三出席菁英會的論壇時大談創新及創科，他今早又自誇自己有3場演講，首兩場是與設計及知識產權有關。提到出席知識產權的活動時，他特別指該活動共有2,800人參加，一半為外國人，另一半則為中國人和港人，然後指外界對內地的印象可能是有關侵犯知識產業權、賣假貨等，但其實在中國新登記的知識產權數字已經超美成世界第一，而且增長十分快，香港的在這方面的角色是做知識產權轉移。<br />\n<br />\n梁再重申推動發展香港經濟值得重視，因為不發展經濟難以改善民生，同時他更主動指15/16財政年度有歷來最高的利得稅收益達，達1,400億元，笑稱「多謝大家交稅」。他亦強調自己上任後政府社福開支增加逾50%，領取失業綜援的個案又連續88個月下降，是97年5月以來最低，形容這是值得港人驕傲的事，博得台下一時掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n他又重彈舊調稱自己重視創科和相關工作，指阻礙港人創業的是租金貴的問題，故當局加大土地供應，解決住屋和創業經濟的困難，揚言未來5年九東有800萬呎商業寫字樓面積，長遠則有5,000萬呎供應。<br />\n<br />\n最後他表示過去30多年，港人乘內地改革開放，令本地公司成為全國性公司，未來的數十年有另一東風：一帶一路，呼籲香港要做中國與外國的超級聯繫人，強調與外國城市相比，香港有一國優勢，與內地城市相比香港仍有兩制優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161201&amp;guid=55989781&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161201%26guid%3D55989781%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=35173869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161201%26guid%3D55989781%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=24c0faf8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161201&amp;guid=55989781&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"26b3c355724abb09afd39f5de9209ca66b721e61","tid":16135,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392a347eada78dcfa018d3fa9120d9a70ad8d900","tid":16135,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"71a22fe4dd4633f9300c83d7005b8c8321a44c61","tid":16135,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:41:18.000Z","msg":"唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583d28f31fb1b6d5bcc4776a661b01574a0c79ce","tid":16135,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66720feb5a7fd904511fd60ae680b925ca1cbcee","tid":16135,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:10:07.000Z","msg":"咪登記哂個啲未係中國登記既知識產權<br />\n等人地一打入中國市場就告鳩人搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae7c6988448e7c65da12f50536941400bf1507d","tid":16135,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:19:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">另一半則為中國人和港人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed0cb23055d64804aa094f5230dff51b91fff1a","tid":16135,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T12:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7ler4sto\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7ler4sto&h=7860b5e5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}